snippet.title: Pango gameplay (PC Game, 1983)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Pango, Dos PC game produced by Coreland in 1983 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/pango/4217/
Struggling with the controls in this old-school Boulderdash-style puzzle game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
